tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  feedback_id UUID,
  customer_id UUID,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  submitted_at TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (feedback_id)
)

CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50),
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE service_insights (
    insight_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feedback_id INT,
    insight_text TEXT,
    insight_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (feedback_id) REFERENCES customer_feedback(feedback_id)
);

CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
	feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	customer_id UUID,
	feedback_text TEXT,
	rating INT,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback_responses (
	response_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	feedback_id UUID,
	response_text TEXT,
	responder_name VARCHAR,
	response_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback_analysis (
	analysis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
	feedback_id UUID,
	sentiment_score FLOAT,
	keywords TEXT[],
	analysis_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_date DATE,
  feedback_rating INT,
  feedback_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerReview (
  review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id UUID,
  review_date DATE,
  review_rating INT,
  review_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE FeedbackAnalysis (
  analysis_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id UUID,
  analysis_date DATE,
  analysis_result TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE FeedbackInsights (
  insight_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  insight_date DATE,
  feedback_id UUID,
  insight_text TEXT
)
